ygData.messageBody:
That vaguely rings a bell, but I can't remember the circumstances behind it.  Will have to ask Erdene if she remembers that.  I think it had something to do with my wulf tail that she kept for me while I was in Japan.  She held the tail for ransom and said that I would have to sing to get it back.  I did finalyl recently get the tail back.  but I really can't remember what the song was.
 
I will send you the lyrics to Broken Ikon if you want.
 
Wulfric

This has absolutely nothing to do with EQ except to say that I had to take a break from playing recently to work on this one.
 
Basically when I'm not out slaying orcs, sometimes I can be found practicing guitar, and occasionally I like to compose music and record it.
 
So I just thought you all mightbe interested in hearing my latest project.  I think it makes great EQ background music....  (uh... right... sure!)
 
But anyway, let me know what you think.
 
http://www.wulfric.com/mp3/Broken_Ikon.mp3
 
 
This song is my own original work and not offered for any profitary reason.  Meaning you dont have to pay anything to download it.  I only ask that credit is given where credit is due.
 
 
Wulfric
